SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD    
Date: Wednesday 1st January 2014

Gary Lineker presents highlights of the ten New Year's Day fixtures in the Premier League. Manchester United and Tottenham meet in a heavyweight clash at Old Trafford, while Arsenal host Cardiff, and fellow title hopefuls Manchester City and Chelsea have tough trips to Swansea and Southampton respectively. Elsewhere, West Brom entertain Newcastle and Sunderland take on Aston Villa. The other games are Everton v Stoke, Liverpool v Hull, Fulham v West Ham and Crystal Palace v Norwich.
